channel.title: Can someone help me make a RSPS?
channel.description:
Hello, everyone I want to make a RSPS and I'm having a lot of trouble with it. So...I was wondering if anyone one here knows how to make a RSPS and wouldn't mind helping me make one over Team Viewer.
I have already made a no-ip account, and downloaded the no-ipduc thing and enabled my server.
I need help with port forwarding
I have not yet found a good client/source to use because i want a good one with no problems and stuff because i am no good with code, and would like some cool customs and such.
So if you could help me make it/and put it online, ill make you Co-Owner or Admin depending on how much stuff you know,Also if you know how to code and could teach me how to add customs and stuff / and teach me how to server reset and make people admins and stuff I would really appreciate it.
So if you could post below if you could help me I would really love it.
My aim is: Mea Mea My xbox live gamer tag: We Be Tro11in
Thank-You.
